name: ColorOutputModes

properties.description: Sends a full-color version of the specified pages to the printer, preserving all color values in the original document. Note: Cannot simulate overprint when using this option.
properties.name: COMPOSITE_LEAVE_UNCHANGED

properties.description: Sends grayscale versions of the specified pages to the printer.
properties.name: COMPOSITE_GRAY

properties.description: Sends full-color versions of the specified pages to the printer.
properties.name: COMPOSITE_RGB

properties.description: Sends full-color versions of the specified pages to the printer. Note: Available only for PostScript printers.
properties.name: COMPOSITE_CMYK

properties.description: Sends PostScript information for each of the required separations to the printer. Note: Available only for PostScript printers.
properties.name: SEPARATIONS

properties.name: INRIP_SEPARATIONS
